details.2114298826: I have lived in Urbana since 1997.  I moved here to attend the University of Illinois and never left the Champaign-Urbana area!  I am a single dad, sharing custody of my youngest of three daughters with my ex-wife.  My youngest daughter is Grace. Grace is a senior this year at Urbana High School. My oldest daughter, Liliana, currently lives in Tampa, FL. She has lived in Tampa since 2013. My middle daughter, Magdalena, is a student at Knox College in Galesburg, IL.
